Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:13.09,Yahei-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是这样,总有一天会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:14.79,Yahei-1920x1080,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}遗憾的是
